## ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
## Mobile touch overlay for Camiel.
##
## Layout:
##   Left 35 % of screen → virtual joystick (walk / run)
##   Right 65 % of screen → action buttons: Jump (bottom-right),
##                            Sit (middle-right), Sleep (top-right)
##
## MobileController (autoload) owns this CanvasLayer; this scene is a child
## of MobileController/TouchLayer so it shares the same input routing.
## ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

[node name="MobileJoystick" type="CanvasLayer"]

## ── Touch layer: joystick + action buttons (mobile only) ─────────────────────
[node name="TouchLayer" type="CanvasLayer" parent="."]

## ── Virtual joystick (bottom-left) ───────────────────────────────────────────
[node name="JoystickArea" type="Control" parent="TouchLayer"]
unique_name_in_owner = true
anchors_preset = 2
anchor_top = 1.0
anchor_bottom = 1.0
offset_left = 24.0
offset_top = -280.0
offset_right = 280.0
offset_bottom = -24.0
grow_vertical = 0

[node name="Base" type="Panel" parent="TouchLayer/JoystickArea"]
layout_mode = 1
anchors_preset = 8
anchor_left = 0.5
anchor_top = 0.5
anchor_right = 0.5
anchor_bottom = 0.5
offset_left = -100.0
offset_top = -100.0
offset_right = 100.0
offset_bottom = 100.0
grow_horizontal = 2
grow_vertical = 2
pivot_offset = Vector2(100, 100)
mouse_filter = 2  ## Control.MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE — let touches pass through
theme_override_styles/normal = SubResource("StyleBoxFlat_base")

[node name="Tip" type="Panel" parent="TouchLayer/JoystickArea/Base"]
unique_name_in_owner = true
layout_mode = 1
anchors_preset = 8
anchor_left = 0.5
anchor_top = 0.5
anchor_right = 0.5
anchor_bottom = 0.5
offset_left = -40.0
offset_top = -40.0
offset_right = 40.0
offset_bottom = 40.0
grow_horizontal = 2
grow_vertical = 2
pivot_offset = Vector2(40, 40)
mouse_filter = 2
theme_override_styles/normal = SubResource("StyleBoxFlat_tip")

## ── Action buttons (bottom-right cluster) ─────────────────────────────────────
[node name="ActionLayer" type="CanvasLayer" parent="."]

## Jump button — bottom-right, largest
[node name="JumpButton" type="Button" parent="ActionLayer"]
unique_name_in_owner = true
anchors_preset = 2
anchor_top = 1.0
anchor_bottom = 1.0
offset_left = -200.0
offset_top = -180.0
offset_right = -56.0
offset_bottom = -56.0
grow_vertical = 0
text = "⬆  spring"
flat = true
mouse_filter = 2  ## Control.MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE — MobileController reads position

[node name="JumpPanel" type="Panel" parent="ActionLayer/JumpButton"]
layout_mode = 1
anchors_preset = 15
anchor_right = 1.0
anchor_bottom = 1.0
grow_horizontal = 2
grow_vertical = 2
mouse_filter = 2
theme_override_styles/normal = SubResource("StyleBoxFlat_button_norm")
theme_override_styles/pressed = SubResource("StyleBoxFlat_button_pressed")

